6:
Oho! I spy with my little eyes... A
beauty beyond compare!
11: Owie! Waaah, it hurts so baaad!
14:
Uh... You're a Sheephird, right? Why
are you pretending to be a kid?
That's just weird...
18:
Dammit! What kinda lady wouldn't
fall for a pretty face like mine?
26:
O-of course it is! You know me,
always cool, calm, collected... and
handsome to boot!
51:
Are you dense?! You saw that gaze
of hers. Those teary eyes... Those
trembling lips...
54:
Heh... How cruel of me. I should have
noticed her feelings long ago...
58:
Anyway, I'm gonna go grace her
with a date! And don't you dare get
in my way! Bye-bye, losers!
64:
Hey, Stella! Mind helping me find
something stolen from me?
72:
Great! Then let's make our way over
to the rendezvous!
78:
That kid... Just where is he planning
on taking Stella?
81:
Come on, I'm sure they're fine on
their own...
85:
Are you mad?! You mean to tell me
you're not the least bit worried
about Stella?
101:
Just thinking about you makes my
heart skip a beat.
104: Oh dear. Should we go see a doctor?
109:
No! I mean... Oh, you're so innocent,
Stella... And that's just part of your
charm!
112: This place should be perfect... Stella.
118:
Think you could take a gander at
this card as well?
126:
I have found that which was stolen
from me. 'Twas my heart, and you,
baby, are the thief. ...Barf. You wrote
this without cringing? How?
131: Aaah! That wasn't meant for you!
136: What are you all doing here?
140:
Yeah! I thought I told you guys to
butt out!
150:
Tch, I wasn't expecting an audience,
but whatever! Stella!
155:
I'm just going to lay it all out, and I'll
take whatever answer I get! You're...
in love me with me, aren't you?
164:
I certainly LIKE you, but I do not like
you in the way you are hoping.
182:
I would never let something as
insignificant as this get me down!
186:
Stella, make no mistake—I WILL
make you fall in love with me! Until
then, adieu!
190:
Well, at least he's not feeling
defeated. That's good, right?
193: He didn't learn a damn thing, did he?
